00018  * File:        gport.h
00019  * Details:     This file defines common error codes to be shared
00020  *                              between API layers.

00022  *             Its contents are not used directly by applications;

00027 #ifndef _SHR_GPORT_H
00028 #define _SHR_GPORT_H
00029 
00030 /*
00031  * Defines:
00032  *     _SHR_GPORT_*
00033  * Purpose:
00034  *     GPORT (Generic port) definitions. GPORT can be used to specify
00035  *     a {module, port} pair, trunk, and other port types.
00036  */
00037 
00038 #define _SHR_GPORT_NONE             (0)
00039 #define _SHR_GPORT_INVALID         (-1)
00040 #define _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_LOCAL               1  /* Port on local unit     */
00041 #define _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_MODPORT             2  /* Module ID and port     */
00042 #define _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_TRUNK               3  /* Trunk ID               */
00043 #define _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_LOCAL_CPU           5  /* CPU destination        */
00044 #define _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_UCAST_QUEUE_GROUP   9  /* Queue Group            */
00045 #define _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_MCAST              11  /* Multicast Set          */
00046 #define _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_MCAST_QUEUE_GROUP  12  /* Multicast Queue Group  */
00047 #define _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_SCHEDULER          13  /* Scheduler              */
00048 #define _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_MIRROR             15  /* Mirror destination.    */
00049 #define _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_CHILD              20  /* Child port             */
00050 #define _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_EGRESS_GROUP       21  /* Egress group port      */
00051 #define _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_EGRESS_CHILD       22  /* Egress child port      */
00052 #define _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_EGRESS_MODPORT     23  /* Egress Mod and port    */
00053 #define _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_UCAST_SUBSCRIBER_QUEUE_GROUP  24  /* Local Queue Group */
00054 #define _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_MCAST_SUBSCRIBER_QUEUE_GROUP  25  /* Local Multicast Queue Group  */
00055 #define _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_COSQ               30  /* cosq gport */
00056 #define _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_PROFILE            40
00057 #define _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_DESTMOD_QUEUE_GROUP      41 /* DMVOQ gport */
00058 
00059 #define _SHR_COSQ_GPORT_COMMON_QUEUE_BITS 18
00060 #define _SHR_COSQ_GPORT_COMMON_QUEUE_MASK ((1 << _SHR_COSQ_GPORT_COMMON_QUEUE_BITS) - 1)
00061 #define _SHR_COSQ_GPORT_COMMON_CORE_BITS 3
00062 #define _SHR_COSQ_GPORT_COMMON_CORE_MASK ((1 << _SHR_COSQ_GPORT_COMMON_CORE_BITS) - 1)
00063 #define _SHR_COSQ_GPORT_COMMON_ALL_CORES_VALUE _SHR_COSQ_GPORT_COMMON_CORE_MASK
00064 #define _SHR_COSQ_GPORT_COMMON_CORE_SHIFT _SHR_COSQ_GPORT_COMMON_QUEUE_BITS
00065 
00066 #define _SHR_CORE_ALL -17
00067 #define _SHR_CORE_FIELD2ID(field) ((field) != _SHR_COSQ_GPORT_COMMON_ALL_CORES_VALUE ? field : _SHR_CORE_ALL)
00068 #define _SHR_CORE_ID2FIELD(id) ((id) != _SHR_CORE_ALL ? id : _SHR_COSQ_GPORT_COMMON_ALL_CORES_VALUE)
00069 
00070 #define _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_SHIFT                           26
00071 #define _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_MASK                            0x3f
00072 
00073 #define _SHR_GPORT_MODID_SHIFT                          11
00074 #define _SHR_GPORT_MODID_MASK                           0x7fff
00075 #define _SHR_GPORT_PORT_SHIFT                           0
00076 #define _SHR_GPORT_PORT_MASK                            0x7ff
00077 #define _SHR_GPORT_TRUNK_SHIFT                          0
00078 #define _SHR_GPORT_TRUNK_MASK                           0x3ffffff
00079 #define _SHR_GPORT_UCAST_QUEUE_GROUP_SHIFT              0
00080 #define _SHR_GPORT_UCAST_QUEUE_GROUP_MASK               0x3ffffff
00081 #define _SHR_GPORT_UCAST_QUEUE_GROUP_QID_SHIFT          0
00082 #define _SHR_GPORT_UCAST_QUEUE_GROUP_QID_MASK           0x3fff
00083 #define _SHR_GPORT_UCAST_QUEUE_GROUP_SYSPORTID_SHIFT    14
00084 #define _SHR_GPORT_UCAST_QUEUE_GROUP_SYSPORTID_MASK     0xfff
00085 #define _SHR_GPORT_MCAST_QUEUE_GROUP_QID_SHIFT          0
00086 #define _SHR_GPORT_MCAST_QUEUE_GROUP_QID_MASK           0x3fff
00087 #define _SHR_GPORT_MCAST_QUEUE_GROUP_SYSPORTID_SHIFT    14
00088 #define _SHR_GPORT_MCAST_QUEUE_GROUP_SYSPORTID_MASK     0xfff
00089 #define _SHR_GPORT_SCHEDULER_SHIFT                      0
00090 #define _SHR_GPORT_SCHEDULER_MASK                       0x7fffff
00091 #define _SHR_GPORT_SCHEDULER_CORE_SHIFT                 23
00092 #define _SHR_GPORT_SCHEDULER_CORE_MASK                  _SHR_COSQ_GPORT_COMMON_CORE_MASK
00093 #define _SHR_GPORT_SCHEDULER_NODE_SHIFT                 0
00094 #define _SHR_GPORT_SCHEDULER_NODE_MASK                  0xfffff
00095 #define _SHR_GPORT_MIRROR_SHIFT                         0
00096 #define _SHR_GPORT_MIRROR_MASK                          0xffff

00098 #define _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_TRAP                            ((_SHR_GPORT_TYPE_LOCAL_CPU << 1) | 1) /* This will mark the CPU type, and
00099                                                                                                   the 1st bit in the value to indicate trap */
00100 #define _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_TRAP_SHIFT                      (_SHR_GPORT_TYPE_SHIFT-1)   /* 25 */
00101 #define _SHR_GPORT_TRAP_ID_SHIFT                         0
00102 #define _SHR_GPORT_TRAP_ID_MASK                          0xfff
00103 #define _SHR_GPORT_TRAP_STRENGTH_SHIFT                       12
00104 #define _SHR_GPORT_TRAP_STRENGTH_MASK                        0xf
00105 #define _SHR_GPORT_TRAP_SNOOP_STRENGTH_SHIFT             16
00106 #define _SHR_GPORT_TRAP_SNOOP_STRENGTH_MASK              0xf
00107 
00108 #define _SHR_GPORT_IS_MODPORT(_gport)    \
00109         (((_gport) >> _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_SHIFT) == _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_MODPORT)
00110 
00111 #define _SHR_GPORT_MODPORT_SET(_gport, _module, _port)                       \
00112         ((_gport) = (_SHR_GPORT_TYPE_MODPORT   << _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_SHIFT)   | \
00113          (((_module) & _SHR_GPORT_MODID_MASK)  << _SHR_GPORT_MODID_SHIFT)  | \
00114          (((_port) & _SHR_GPORT_PORT_MASK)     << _SHR_GPORT_PORT_SHIFT))
00115 
00116 #define _SHR_GPORT_MODPORT_MODID_GET(_gport)    \
00117         (((_gport) >> _SHR_GPORT_MODID_SHIFT) & _SHR_GPORT_MODID_MASK)
00118 
00119 #define _SHR_GPORT_MODPORT_PORT_GET(_gport)     \
00120         (((_gport) >> _SHR_GPORT_PORT_SHIFT) & _SHR_GPORT_PORT_MASK)
00121 
00122 #define _SHR_GPORT_IS_TRUNK(_gport)    \
00123         (((_gport) >> _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_SHIFT) == _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_TRUNK)
00124 
00125 #define _SHR_GPORT_TRUNK_SET(_gport, _trunk_id)                              \
00126         ((_gport) = (_SHR_GPORT_TYPE_TRUNK      << _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_SHIFT)  | \
00127          (((_trunk_id) & _SHR_GPORT_TRUNK_MASK) << _SHR_GPORT_TRUNK_SHIFT))
00128 
00129 #define _SHR_GPORT_TRUNK_GET(_gport)   \
00130         (((_gport) >> _SHR_GPORT_TRUNK_SHIFT) & _SHR_GPORT_TRUNK_MASK)
00131 
00132 #define _SHR_GPORT_IS_SCHEDULER(_gport)    \
00133         (((_gport) >> _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_SHIFT) == _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_SCHEDULER)
00134 
00135 #define _SHR_GPORT_SCHEDULER_SET(_gport, _id)                            \
00136          _SHR_GPORT_SCHEDULER_CORE_SET(_gport, _id, _SHR_CORE_ALL)
00137 
00138 #define _SHR_GPORT_SCHEDULER_GET(_gport)   \
00139          (((_gport) >> _SHR_GPORT_SCHEDULER_SHIFT) & _SHR_GPORT_SCHEDULER_MASK)
00140 
00141 #define _SHR_GPORT_LOCAL_CPU        \
00142         (_SHR_GPORT_TYPE_LOCAL_CPU << _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_SHIFT)
00143 
00144 #define _SHR_GPORT_IS_UCAST_QUEUE_GROUP(_gport)    \
00145         (((_gport) >> _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_SHIFT) == _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_UCAST_QUEUE_GROUP)

00147 #define _SHR_GPORT_UCAST_QUEUE_GROUP_SET(_gport, _qid)                           \
00148              _SHR_GPORT_UCAST_QUEUE_GROUP_SYSQID_SET(_gport,                      \
00149              _SHR_GPORT_UCAST_QUEUE_GROUP_SYSPORTID_MASK, \
00150               _qid)
00151 
00152 #define _SHR_GPORT_UCAST_QUEUE_GROUP_SYSQID_SET(_gport, _sysport_id, _qid)                       \
00153         ((_gport) = (_SHR_GPORT_TYPE_UCAST_QUEUE_GROUP << _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_SHIFT)   | \
00154          (((_sysport_id) & _SHR_GPORT_UCAST_QUEUE_GROUP_SYSPORTID_MASK)  << _SHR_GPORT_UCAST_QUEUE_GROUP_SYSPORTID_SHIFT)  | \
00155          (((_qid) & _SHR_GPORT_UCAST_QUEUE_GROUP_QID_MASK)     << _SHR_GPORT_UCAST_QUEUE_GROUP_QID_SHIFT))
00156 
00157 #define _SHR_GPORT_IS_MCAST_QUEUE_GROUP(_gport) \
00158         (((_gport) >> _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_SHIFT) == _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_MCAST_QUEUE_GROUP)

00160 #define _SHR_GPORT_IS_COSQ(_gport) \

00162 
00163 #define  _SHR_GPORT_SCHEDULER_CORE_GET(_gport) \
00164         _SHR_CORE_FIELD2ID((((_gport) >> _SHR_GPORT_SCHEDULER_CORE_SHIFT) & _SHR_GPORT_SCHEDULER_CORE_MASK))
00165 
00166 #define _SHR_GPORT_SCHEDULER_CORE_SET(_gport, _scheduler_id, _core_id)       \
00167         ((_gport) = (_SHR_GPORT_TYPE_SCHEDULER << _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_SHIFT)  | \
00168         (((_scheduler_id) & _SHR_GPORT_SCHEDULER_MASK) << _SHR_GPORT_SCHEDULER_SHIFT) | \
00169         (((_SHR_CORE_ID2FIELD(_core_id)) & _SHR_GPORT_SCHEDULER_CORE_MASK) << _SHR_GPORT_SCHEDULER_CORE_SHIFT))
00170 
00171 #define _SHR_GPORT_SCHEDULER_NODE_SET(_gport, _level, _node)    \
00172          ((_gport) = (_SHR_GPORT_TYPE_SCHEDULER << _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_SHIFT)  | \
00173           (((_level) & _SHR_GPORT_SCHEDULER_LEVEL_MASK) << _SHR_GPORT_SCHEDULER_LEVEL_SHIFT) | \
00174           (((_node) & _SHR_GPORT_SCHEDULER_NODE_MASK) << _SHR_GPORT_SCHEDULER_NODE_SHIFT))
00175 
00176 #define _SHR_GPORT_SCHEDULER_NODE_GET(_gport)   \
00177          (((_gport) >> _SHR_GPORT_SCHEDULER_NODE_SHIFT) & _SHR_GPORT_SCHEDULER_NODE_MASK)
00178 
00179 #define _SHR_GPORT_TRAP_SET(_gport, _trap_id, _trap_strength, _snoop_strength)     \
00180         ((_gport) = (_SHR_GPORT_TYPE_TRAP << _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_TRAP_SHIFT)   |      \
00181          (((_trap_id) & _SHR_GPORT_TRAP_ID_MASK) << _SHR_GPORT_TRAP_ID_SHIFT)  |    \
00182          (((_trap_strength) & _SHR_GPORT_TRAP_STRENGTH_MASK) << _SHR_GPORT_TRAP_STRENGTH_SHIFT)  |  \
00183          (((_snoop_strength) & _SHR_GPORT_TRAP_SNOOP_STRENGTH_MASK) << _SHR_GPORT_TRAP_SNOOP_STRENGTH_SHIFT) )
00184

00224 /* for multicast queue gports representing queue ID + core ID */
00225 #define _SHR_GPORT_MCAST_QUEUE_GROUP_QUEUE_SET(_gport, _qid) \
00226         ((_gport) = (_SHR_GPORT_TYPE_MCAST_QUEUE_GROUP << _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_SHIFT) | \
00227          (_SHR_COSQ_GPORT_COMMON_ALL_CORES_VALUE << _SHR_COSQ_GPORT_COMMON_CORE_SHIFT) | \

00229 
00230 #define _SHR_GPORT_MCAST_QUEUE_GROUP_CORE_QUEUE_SET(_gport, _core, _qid) \
00231         ((_gport) = (_SHR_GPORT_TYPE_MCAST_QUEUE_GROUP << _SHR_GPORT_TYPE_SHIFT) | \
00232          (_SHR_CORE_ID2FIELD(_core) << _SHR_COSQ_GPORT_COMMON_CORE_SHIFT) | \
00233          (((_qid) & _SHR_COSQ_GPORT_COMMON_QUEUE_MASK) << _SHR_GPORT_MCAST_QUEUE_GROUP_QID_SHIFT))
00234 
00235 #define _SHR_GPORT_MCAST_QUEUE_GROUP_QUEUE_GET(_gport) \
00236         (_SHR_GPORT_MCAST_QUEUE_GROUP_SYSPORTID_GET(_gport) == _SHR_GPORT_MCAST_QUEUE_GROUP_SYSPORTID_MASK ? \
00237         _SHR_GPORT_MCAST_QUEUE_GROUP_QID_GET(_gport) : \
00238         (((_gport) >> _SHR_GPORT_MCAST_QUEUE_GROUP_QID_SHIFT) & _SHR_COSQ_GPORT_COMMON_QUEUE_MASK))
